{
  "texts": [
    "Autoencoders have diverse applications in fault diagnosis, intrusion detection, and hyperspectral imaging.",
    "They help detect faults in systems, identify network intrusions, and enhance the analysis of hyperspectral data for applications like remote sensing.",
    "Different autoencoder versions are tailored to meet specific challenges in these domains.",
    "Fault diagnosis is the process of identifying, isolating, and characterizing faults or anomalies in a system or machine.",
    "It involves analyzing the behavior of the system or machine and identifying any deviations from normal or expected behavior."
  ]
}